{
  "stem": "21139.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As small as you can-- not to-- you know, they shouldn't ask you where you come from, where-- any of this.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it didn't happen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it-- the Germans did come.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were bombed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At night, we were bombed by the Americans, and during the day, by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were-- once, I remember I was running through the shelter and for out-- that was outside the house, and a bomb went right over my head.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I could see it so clearly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it-- it exploded a little bit away-- quite a bit away, I should say.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it was scary to see it right over your head.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so-- and then, when I were-- we were in Saint-Jean.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was already later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you could see it-- it's going towards the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a lot of underground movement going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was a Dr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Almen who used to come to the people where I worked.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it's-- I believe the man where I worked, he was participating in all of these activities.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he-- but the Germans caught him and executed him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Almen.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, as the war close-- got-- was close to the end, they caught some Germans and they hanged them in the village square.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember Amelie and Margot saying that I should come and watch, but I-- but I couldn't do that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I didn't and I couldn't-- and I couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember that so well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then there was that family that market worked for, where the husband was a doctor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was in the marines and-- a doctor in the marines.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
